{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 74,
    "name": "سُورَةُ المُدَّثِّرِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Muddaththir",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Cloaked One",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 56,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5496,
        "text": "蓋被的人啊！",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5497,
        "text": "你應當起來，你應當警告，",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5498,
        "text": "你應當頌揚你的主宰，",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5499,
        "text": "你應當洗滌你的衣服，",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5500,
        "text": "你應當遠離污穢，",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5501,
        "text": "你不要施恩而求厚報，",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5502,
        "text": "你應當為你的主而堅忍。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5503,
        "text": "當號角被吹嚮的時候，",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5504,
        "text": "在那時，將有一個艱難的日子。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5505,
        "text": "那個日子對不信道的人們，是不容易渡過的。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5506,
        "text": "你讓我獨自處治我所創造的那個人吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5507,
        "text": "我賞賜他豐富的財產，",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5508,
        "text": "和在跟前的子嗣，",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5509,
        "text": "我提高了他的聲望，",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5510,
        "text": "而他還冀望我再多加賞賜。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5511,
        "text": "絕不然，他確實是反對我的跡象的，",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5512,
        "text": "我將使他遭受苦難。",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5513,
        "text": "他碓已思考，確已計劃。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5514,
        "text": "但無論他怎樣計劃，他是被棄絕的。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5515,
        "text": "無論他怎樣計劃，他終是被棄絕的。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5516,
        "text": "他看一看，",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5517,
        "text": "然後皺眉蹙額，",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5518,
        "text": "然後高傲地轉過身去，",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5519,
        "text": "而且說：「這只是傳習的魔術，",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5520,
        "text": "這只是凡人的言辭。」",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5521,
        "text": "我將使他墮入火獄，",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5522,
        "text": "你怎能知道火獄是什麼？",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5523,
        "text": "它不讓任何物存在，不許任何物留下，",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5524,
        "text": "它燒灼肌膚。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5525,
        "text": "管理它的，共計十九名。",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5526,
        "text": "我只將管理火獄的成天神，我只以他們的數目，考驗不信道的人們，以便曾受天經的人們認清，而信道的人們更加篤信；以免曾受天經的人們和信道的人們懷疑；以便心中有病者和不信道者說：「真主設這個譬喻做什麼？」真主這樣使他所意欲的人誤入迷途，使他所意欲的人遵循正路。只有你的主，能知道他的軍隊，這只是人類的教訓。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 510,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5527,
        "text": "真的，以月亮盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5528,
        "text": "以逝去的黑夜盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5529,
        "text": "以顯照的黎明盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5530,
        "text": "火獄確是一個大難，",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5531,
        "text": "可以警告人類，",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5532,
        "text": "警告你們中欲前進者或欲後退者；",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5533,
        "text": "各人將因自己的營謀而作抵押，",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5534,
        "text": "惟幸福的人們除外。",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5535,
        "text": "他們在樂園中互相詢問，",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5536,
        "text": "問犯罪人們的情狀，",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5537,
        "text": "「你們為什麼墮入火獄呢？」",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5538,
        "text": "他們說：「我們沒有禮拜，",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5539,
        "text": "也沒有濟貧，",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5540,
        "text": "我們與妄言的人們一道妄言，",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5541,
        "text": "我們否認報應日，",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5542,
        "text": "一直到死亡降臨了我們。」",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 576,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5543,
        "text": "說情者的說情，將無益於他們。",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5544,
        "text": "他們怎麼退避這教訓呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5545,
        "text": "他們好像一群驚慌的驢子，",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5546,
        "text": "剛逃避了一隻獅子一樣。",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5547,
        "text": "不然，他們中的每個人都希望獲得一些展開的天經。",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5548,
        "text": "絕不然，他們不畏懼後世！",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5549,
        "text": "真的，這《古蘭經》確是一個教誨！",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5550,
        "text": "誰願意，誰記憶它，",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5551,
        "text": "他們只因真主的意欲而記憶它。他是應受敬畏的，他是宜於赦宥的。",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 577,
        "ruku": 511,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
